<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang = "en">
    <%- include('../partials/head.partial.ejs', {title: 'Home'}) %>
    <body>
        <%- include('../partials/nav.partial.ejs') %>
        
        <section class = "flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-y-5 text-center">
            <h1>Welcome to Orto<b>Plan</b></h1>
            <div class = "flex-col-container">
                <p class = "w-5/6">
                    Designed to make it simple and convenient for you to schedule and keep track of your plants' care, so you can focus on what matters most - enjoying your greenery.
                    Let's take care of your plants together!
                </p>
                <hr class = "animate-showHide origin-center green-line w-40">
            </div>
        </section>
        <img src = "/assets/icons/grass.webp" alt = "Grass">
        <section class = "app-description">
            <div>
                <b>Plants care & more</b>
                <h1>PLANT CARE MADE EASY</h1>
            </div>
            <p>
                With OrtoPlan, you can easily <span class = "text-primary">manage your plantations</span> and stay on top of their care.
                Our application allows you to <span class = "text-primary">add, edit, and remove plants</span> from your inventory, and track their watering and fertilization schedules.
                You'll also receive <span class = "text-primary">forecast warning notifications</span> to help you prepare for potential weather-related issues that may affect your plants.
                Plus, you can <span class = "text-primary">view upcoming planned treatments</span> for each plant, so you know exactly when and how to care for them.
                This makes it easy to keep your plants healthy and thriving.
            </p>
        </section>
        <img class = "w-full my-11 sm:w-4/5" src = "/assets/icons/tree.webp" alt = "Tree branch">
        <section class = "app-description">
            <div>
                <b>Effortless plants management</b>
                <h1>PLANTS TREATMENT</h1>
            </div>
            <p>
                Effortlessly manage your plants' treatments with OrtoPlan.
                Our application allows you to easily remove, and plan all of your plant's  treatments with ease.
                You can <span class = "text-primary">set a starting date, recurrence, and even quick notes</span> for each treatment, so everything is organized and streamlined.
                Plus, you'll <span class = "text-primary">receive notifications</span> when it's time to administer each treatment, ensuring that your plants receive the care they need, when they need it.
            </p>
        </section>
        <img src = "/assets/icons/grass.webp" alt = "Tree branch">
        <section class = "app-description flex flex-col text-center items-center gap-y-5">
            <h1>What are you waiting for?</h1>
            <div class = "flex-col-container">
                <p class = "w-5/6">Join our community full of of satisfied customers who are already making their green life easier by using OrtoPlan!</p>
                <hr class = "animate-showHide origin-center green-line w-36">
            </div>
            <div class = "cardsContainer">
                <div class = "customCard">
                    <figure>
                        <img src = "/assets/icons/reviewer_1.webp" alt = "Positive review">
                    </figure>
                    <div class = "cardContent">
                        <h2>Idea Verde</h2>
                        <p>
                            I love this app! It makes it so easy to keep track of my plants' treatments.
                            I no longer have to worry about forgetting to water or fertilize.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class = "customCard">
                    <figure>
                        <img src = "/assets/icons/reviewer_2.webp" alt = "Another positive review">
                    </figure>
                    <div class = "cardContent">
                        <h2>Luigi Ciavarella</h2>
                        <p>
                            This app is a game changer for me as a busy gardener.
                            It allows me to easily plan and schedule my plants' care, and the notifications are so convenient.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class = "customCard">
                    <figure>
                        <img src = "/assets/icons/reviewer_3.webp" alt = "Third positive review">
                    </figure>
                    <div class = "cardContent">
                        <h2>Pasquale Ficelo</h2>
                        <p>
                            I was skeptical at first, but this app has really helped me improve my plant care.
                            The customizable settings and treatment planning features are great.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <%- include('../partials/footer.partial.ejs', {
            includeScripts: false
        }) %>
    </body>
</html>